WEBVTT

01:27:06.256 --> 01:27:08.048
Imagine how anxious I am.

01:27:09.256 --> 01:27:11.339
After so many years, I came back to India,

01:27:12.423 --> 01:27:14.798
and he stole my memory and fled.

01:27:15.964 --> 01:27:17.631
Find him, wherever he is.

01:27:18.089 --> 01:27:18.964
Find him.

01:27:24.839 --> 01:27:25.673
Shankar!

01:27:30.256 --> 01:27:31.464
Listen, look... look here,

01:27:32.839 --> 01:27:34.506
Who made this hole?

01:27:34.548 --> 01:27:36.631
Brother, they insert another SIM in you, brother.

01:27:36.756 --> 01:27:38.464
Never mind, let them do it,
but this time, ask them to recharge it.

01:27:38.631 --> 01:27:41.881
Hey, it's not a SIM card; they've put
such a big hard disk inside.
